articles.title: About
articles.description: Lover of dogs, cold brew, and all things data
articles.contents:
Ryan Plain
Data Analyst at Southwest Airlines. Graduate student studying Analytics at Georgia Tech.
I created this to show things I have been working on, either personal projects or for school. A goal for 2021 is to take part in Tidy Tuesday to practice implementation of new models and packages.
Get in touch with me on Twitter @RyanPlain
